tab2.text1:
/Suicide - Kills you instantly 
 /unstuck - Teleports you a close distance from where you are when stuck 
 /getuniqueID - Gives you the UniqueID of your Account 
 /discord - Opens the Discord 
 /ccc 0 Copies a CCC Command into your Clipboard 
 /donate - Opens the Shop of the Server in your Browser 
 /unstuckcorpse - Attempts to unstuck your Corpse, must be nearby 
 /vote - Opens the Voting-Link
